 12 galaxies that hosted 2 or more SNe~Ia, we find\nthat when using SNe~Ia, and after accounting for all sources of observational\nerror, one gets consistency in distance to 3 percent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Apr 2020 18:06:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-10"}
