find that, if possible at\nall, quantum computation using measurement-based braiding in the quasi-Majorana\nregime would be plagued with errors introduced by the measurement processes\nthemselves, while such errors are significantly less likely in a scheme\ninvolving topological MZMs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Apr 2020 18:06:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
