lpha}$ when $\\beta$ is\na Pisot number and when $\\beta$ is the $n$-th root of a Pisot number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 09:32:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-29"}
