sults as SCAN for all properties examined with the\nexception of atomization energies which are somewhat worse in rSCAN. On the\nother hand, SIC-rSCAN gives marginally better performance than SIC-SCAN for\nalmost all properties studied in this work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 10:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-29"}
