at reducing the interfacial orbital hybridization may be used\nas a tunable parameter for the strength of the exchange bias effect in\nall-oxide heterostructures which exhibit a charge transfer mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 15:29:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-29"}
